Joe Davis

Grew up in Eau Claire, WI and moved to Minneapolis for college and they havent been able to get rid of me yet. Applied to the DACSS program to expand the tools available to me in my work, trying to advanced progressive causes and candidates. My wifes name is also Joey. We are called the Joeys. Though it is often confusing, and why I now go by Joe, its not as weird as it seems I swear.
